## Code Style
- TypeScript strict mode
- Functional components only
- Dynamic color logic: never show red alert for 0 spills
- Clinical white card UI, not colorful blocks
- Mobile-first responsive design
- Primary CTA: "Request Lead Survey Quote" (solid blue)
- Secondary CTA: ghost/outline button